In a two-week trip through Italy which included some very pretty places, this was absolutely our favorite.	This was our favorite hotel during our travels by far!	This was our third trip to Venice.	Our room was one of two on the top floor, which sadly the elevator doesn't go to.	The city did not smell during our visit and was cleaner than Rome or Florence.	Great hotel would absolutely recommend this one if you can afford it.	Overall this was a very nice hotel with very good room standards.	This was a little unexpected.	This hotel is an awesome value.	Overall, definitely recommend this hotel.